{"tid":425232,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓網友認證　少女時代太妍飯和IU飯的不同之處","createTime":"2017-10-05T13:59:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T14:06:18.000Z","uid":103309,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a89792309d5a2f99a0ad25998b2788e8d95b79b5","tid":425232,"uid":103309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T13:59:22.000Z","msg":"不同的偶像擁有不同的粉絲？<br />\n<br />\n近日在韓國網絡論壇的一則題爲&ldquo;太妍飯和IU飯的區別&rdquo;的帖子吸引網友眼球。<br />\n<br />\n留帖的網友截下&ldquo;DCInside&rdquo;網站的&ldquo;太妍Gallery（粉絲網）&rdquo;和&ldquo;IU Gallery&rdquo;網頁截圖。帖主在太妍和IU的粉絲網留言提問： &ldquo;如果讓妳們給太妍買60萬元（約台幣18,000元）的裏脊肉妳們會出錢嗎？&rdquo;、&ldquo;妳們能給IU買60萬元（約台幣18,000元）的裏脊肉嗎？&rdquo;收到奇葩回答。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://upload.enewsworld.net/News/Contents/20141121/48872907.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.enewsworld.net%2FNews%2FContents%2F20141121%2F48872907.jpg&h=e86cc343&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n太妍粉絲們紛紛留言：&ldquo;怎麽能不給買呢？&rdquo;、&ldquo;如果能見面的話&rdquo;、&ldquo;開玩笑呢？如果沒有60萬我就算打苦工也要給她買裏脊肉。就算只能見她2小時我也願意&hellip;啊 ，死忠飯的心情原來就是這樣子的..kk&rdquo;展現一種很正常的飯的反應。<br />\n<br />\n而IU的粉絲們則留言表示：&ldquo;瘋了嗎？幹嘛買給她？我自己一個人吃&rdquo;、&ldquo;幹嘛請她吃？&rdquo;、&ldquo;爲什麽要請吃賺幾億的孩子？如果見面的話她請我才對&rdquo;、&ldquo;有60萬的話，我就買衣服和鞋子&rdquo;、&ldquo;kkkk 知恩買給我們才對&rdquo;、&ldquo;能買到幾盤披薩&rdquo;、&ldquo;這種事發生的可能性是0&rdquo;搞笑的意見笑噴諸多網友。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://upload.enewsworld.net/News/Contents/20141121/85539095.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.enewsworld.net%2FNews%2FContents%2F20141121%2F85539095.jpg&h=6ffb5c55&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"cc74dcebcb409671c5bdf096f64178d1f8068ede","tid":425232,"uid":7419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:01:20.000Z","msg":"3P"},{"pid":"c0ffa4c4b2fd2b3a607f23396c1e9b53b0812841","tid":425232,"uid":7008,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:02:02.000Z","msg":"迷一班30歲既阿嬸仲要叫少女<br />\n好難相信個腦係完整"},{"pid":"d4fbd4cdaa9fd7f652fa67d3d46a77e150ff746a","tid":425232,"uid":34071,"like":5,"dislike":11,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:04:35.000Z","msg":"垃圾泰妍好多粉都係毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1bd9a054fe05737e2661468534669ca97a17fad","tid":425232,"uid":79059,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:06:18.000Z","msg":"idol飯同歌手飯點會一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}